{
  "$comment": "Root governed-surface contract for the vibe-engineer workspace. Declares the REAL governed product surface (packages, scripts, docs, examples, infra, .github, root config/carrier files) and excludes multi-orchestrator scratch + agent-harness + build-cache trees (.vibe, .pi, .turbo, .vitepress) and the generated lockfile. Authored by FINAL-BUGHUNT FIX (Triad-B).",
